OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1780495874
OL,3,COmagh woman sets up register to
OL,4,Cconnect those in need with carers
OL,6,FAn Omagh woman who experienced the
OL,7,F'overwhelming' pressures on the health
OL,8,Fsystem during a stay in A&E has set up
OL,9,Fa private register to connect carers
OL,10,Fwith those in need.
OL,12,FKerry O'Neill hopes the online system
OL,13,Fwill help with demand and ensure older
OL,14,Fpeople who want to stay at home can
OL,15,Fget the help they require - even if it
OL,16,Fis just a chat.
OL,18,FDemand on social care in Northern
OL,19,FIreland is high and there is a
OL,20,Fshortage of carers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
