PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1780495874
OL,3,COmagh woman sets up register to
OL,4,Cconnect those in need with carers
OL,6,FBrenda Lewsley, also from Omagh, lives
OL,7,Fwith serious complex health issues and
OL,8,Fhas a carer through Direct Payments
OL,9,Ffor two hours, Monday to Wednesday.
OL,11,FThe 77-year-old says she needs more
OL,12,Fhelp and cannot get it.
OL,14,FBrenda told UTV she struggles to get
OL,15,Fout of bed and prepare meals for
OL,16,Fherself.
OL,18,F"I would virtually be bed bound
OL,19,FWednesday to Monday. I have no one,"
OL,20,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1780495874
OL,3,COmagh woman sets up register to
OL,4,Cconnect those in need with carers
OL,6,FHer situation has also impacted her
OL,7,Femotional wellbeing.
OL,9,F"Last year I was really, really bad.
OL,10,FThe depression and the mental health,
OL,11,Fthe panic attacks," Brenda continued.
OL,13,FKerry O'Neill experienced the pressure
OL,14,Fon the system first-hand during a stay
OL,15,Fin an Enniskillen Emergency Department
OL,16,Fin 2025.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
