PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1780495874
OL,3,COmagh woman sets up register to
OL,4,Cconnect those in need with carers
OL,6,FIn a social media video recorded
OL,7,Fduring her stay, she said: "It would
OL,8,Fabsolutely break your heart if you
OL,9,Fcould see the people, especially
OL,10,Felderly people lying on beds in the
OL,11,Fcorridor and staff so overwhelmed.
OL,13,FNow, she has set up a register to
OL,14,Fconnect carers with clients like
OL,15,FBrenda to help with the simple tasks
OL,16,Fthat other carers cannot or do not
OL,17,Fhave the time to do because of demand.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
