PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1780495874
OL,3,COmagh woman sets up register to
OL,4,Cconnect those in need with carers
OL,6,F"Through my cleaning business, the
OL,7,Fworst thing I have noticed is the
OL,8,Fisolation for older people in the
OL,9,Fcommunity.
OL,11,F"They are really really struggling to
OL,12,Fget people to come out and just be
OL,13,Fwith them. Just talk to them. Maybe
OL,14,Fhelp them around the house a little
OL,15,Fbit.
OL,17,F"Carers are completely overwhelmed.
OL,18,F(They have) 15 mins to do the bare
OL,19,Fnecessities, the physical medical care
OL,20,Fthat they need.
OL,26,@zD@ApmzD@Kpn
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
