PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1780495874
OL,3,COmagh woman sets up register to
OL,4,Cconnect those in need with carers
OL,6,F"Then they have to leave to go on to
OL,7,Fthe next one", Kerry said.
OL,9,FThe register is for carers to upload
OL,10,Ftheir profile with details of their
OL,11,Favailability, location and
OL,12,Fqualifications.
OL,14,F"This is specifically for carers to
OL,15,Fupload their profile and say what
OL,16,Ftasks they are willing to do, where
OL,17,Fthey are, what hours.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1780495874
OL,3,COmagh woman sets up register to
OL,4,Cconnect those in need with carers
OL,6,F"They can be qualified or unqualified,
OL,7,Fas someone might just being looking
OL,8,Ffor them to come in and make a cup of
OL,9,Ftea and talk.
OL,11,F"Or they might like them to go to the
OL,12,Fshop for them and bring them their
OL,13,Fshopping because there is no service
OL,14,Flike that.
OL,16,F"People are begging for help and
OL,17,Fessentially, it just means that they
OL,18,Fhave to put a family member in a home
OL,19,Fand they do not want to do that,"
OL,20,FKerry continued.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
